The paper discusses the Coherence Length Diagram (CLD) and its use in image analysis, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR). The paper also mentions the use of optimization analysis and histogram-based methods, which are commonly used in machine learning (cs.MM), information retrieval (cs.IR), and data structures (cs.DS).
